{
  "title": "linux光盘",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">光盘&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">cdrecord -v gracetime=2 dev=/dev/cdrom -eject blank=fast -force 清空一个可复写的光盘内容&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">mkisofs /dev/cdrom &gt; cd.iso 在磁盘上创建一个光盘的iso镜像文件&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">mkisofs /dev/cdrom | gzip &gt; cd_iso.gz 在磁盘上创建一个压缩了的光盘iso镜像文件&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">mkisofs -J -allow-leading-dots -R -V \"Label CD\" -iso-level 4 -o ./cd.iso data_cd 创建一个目录的iso镜像文件&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">cdrecord -v dev=/dev/cdrom cd.iso 刻录一个ISO镜像文件&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">gzip -dc cd_iso.gz | cdrecord dev=/dev/cdrom - 刻录一个压缩了的ISO镜像文件&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">mount -o loop cd.iso /mnt/iso 挂载一个ISO镜像文件&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">cd-paranoia -B 从一个CD光盘转录音轨到 wav 文件中&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">cd-paranoia -- \"-3\" 从一个CD光盘转录音轨到 wav 文件中（参数-3）&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">cdrecord --scanbus 扫描总线以识别scsi通道&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">dd if=/dev/hdc | md5sum 校验一个设备的md5sum编码，例如一张 CD&nbsp;</span></font>"
    }
  ]
}